snippet.title: The Story of Eric Whitacre’s Stopping by Woods on a Snowy Evening
snippet.description:
Join Eric Whitacre and VOCES8 as they share the unusual unfolding of Stopping by Woods on a Snowy Evening.

Get a look into the score here: https://youtu.be/2vp8NarasHY?si=FsM9T1-zd8X6soqA

Music available here: https://giamusic.com/resource/stopping-by-woods-on-a-snowy-evening-printed-music-wjms1232

View VOCES8 full performance here: https://youtu.be/FgcZSiMLjlc?si=jkFTQZwW3_CyTju_
